                        <interp inst="t18420228-1018-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 23.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">JAMES FERNLEY, WILLIAM HENRY FERNLEY, GEORGE FERNLEY</hi> and <hi rend="largeCaps">ABIGAIL DE SOIZA—
